{"tid":668141,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救window loop after bio","createTime":"2018-05-17T10:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T12:00:02.000Z","uid":65547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"041cc2e70459c80bef231d0008f5507c7a894e5f","tid":668141,"uid":65547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"前晚訓前update window<br />\n(其實佢叫左我好多日update我都無理佢)<br />\n但係最終都係update左<br />\n琴日一開機就即刻藍畫面<br />\n好似話係update not complete <br />\n好似有兩個window save 比我揀<br />\n咁我揀返之前嗰個就冇事<br />\n咁臨瞓前閂機又問我up唔update<br />\n我就冇up<br />\n之後今日返到開機就不停率loop<br />\n試過f8 入safe mode 入唔到<br />\n咁三次hard restart 又入唔到<br />\nBoot from usb 又唔得<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/185651_8de8b1dd71d7cd51ee7bdc6d36fcee1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F185651_8de8b1dd71d7cd51ee7bdc6d36fcee1e.png&h=e41dc3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add001d60883468a19d2ce9be33ad5f4b3740e5d","tid":668141,"uid":65547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"係咁見到giga 個menu<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/185845_1f27d17f20ca00f1bb6b5e133e3f28c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F185845_1f27d17f20ca00f1bb6b5e133e3f28c8.png&h=45935095&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a29b074335cdc4bf0cb364eea0d32ae17baa54c","tid":668141,"uid":65547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5660af4b0b6f5dd90b82a331aade8ff6454db480","tid":668141,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote